 12 Semifinal with Win over Arizona State</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/6/womens-basketball-mountaineers-advance-to-big-12-semifinal-with-win-over-arizona-state</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/6/womens-basketball-mountaineers-advance-to-big-12-semifinal-with-win-over-arizona-state</guid><category>Women's Basketball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Sydney Shaw" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/6/030626_Big_12_Tourney_Day_3_TL-58.jpg" /><br /><br />KANSAS CITY, Mo. – The No. 15 West Virginia women's basketball team used an 11-0 run in the late stages of the fourth quarter to get past Arizona State, 67-54, in the quarterfinal of the Phillips 66 Big 12 Tournament on Friday night at T-Mobile Center.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/6/030626_Big_12_Tourney_Day_3_TL-58.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/6/030626_Big_12_Tourney_Day_3_TL-58.jpg"><media:title>Sydney Shaw</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/6/030626_Big_12_Tourney_Day_3_TL-58.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Fri, 6 Mar 2026 21:45:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>9</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58817</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Fall to Columbia in Series Opener</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/6/baseball-mountaineers-fall-to-columbia-in-series-opener</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/6/baseball-mountaineers-fall-to-columbia-in-series-opener</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Brodie Kresser" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_pr