e_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/6/ex1_75.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Fri, 6 Mar 2026 18:15:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>15</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58815</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Wraps Up Big 12 Regular Season at No. 12 Utah with No. 24 BYU</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/6/gymnastics-west-virginia-wraps-up-big-12-regular-season-at-no-12-utah-with-no-24-byu</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/6/gymnastics-west-virginia-wraps-up-big-12-regular-season-at-no-12-utah-with-no-24-byu</guid><category>Gymnastics</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="auden pederson" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/6/022726_GYMN_Coal_Rush_TL-17.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University gymnastics team prepares to wrap up the Big 12 Conference regular season at No. 12 Utah with No. 24 BYU on Saturday, March 7. Action at the Jon M. Huntsman Center in Salt Lake City, Utah, is scheduled for 5 p.m. ET/3 p.m. MT.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/6/022726_GYMN_Coal_Rush_TL-17.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/6/022726_GYMN_Coal_Rush_TL-17.jpg"><media:title>auden pederson</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/6/022726_GYMN_Coal_Rush_TL-17.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Fri, 6 Mar 2026 11:46:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>11</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58814</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Opens Play at Phillips 66 Big 12 Tournament Friday</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/5/womens-basketball-west-virginia-opens-play-at-phillips-66-big-12-championship-friday</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/5/womens-basketball-west-virginia-opens-play-at-phillips-66-big-12-championship-friday</guid><category>Women's Basketball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Gia Cooke" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/5/DSC06674.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University women's basketball team (24-6, 14-4 Big 12) opens postseason play in the Quarterfinal Round of the Phillips 66 Big 12 Women's Basketball Tournament on Friday, March 6. The No. 2-seeded Mountaineers will face No. 10 Arizona State. Tipoff inside the T-Mobile Center in Kansas City, Missouri, is set for 6:30 p.m. ET.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/5/DSC06674.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/5/DSC06674.jpg"><media:title>Gia Cooke</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/5/DSC06674.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Thu, 5 Mar 2026 20:47:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>9</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58813</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Head to Tulsa for 2026 Big 12 Wrestling Championships</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/5/mountaineers-head-to-tulsa-for-2026-big-12-wrestling-championships</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/5/mountaineers-head-to-tulsa-for-2026-big-12-wrestling-championships</guid><category>Wrestling</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="2026 Big 12 Wrestling Championships (interior)" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/5/VTU098